# Important SIEM Components

## Log Collector

Collects logs from devices.

## Correlation Engine

Detects suspicious patterns.

Example:

* Multiple failed logins
* Port scans
* Malware activity

## Dashboard

Displays alerts and system activity.

## Alerting System

Generates warnings for threats.

---

# SIEM Detection Examples

| Activity               | Detection          |
| ---------------------- | ------------------ |
| Failed logins          | Brute force attack |
| Multiple ports scanned | Port scanning      |
| Unusual DNS traffic    | DNS tunneling      |
| Large outbound traffic | Data exfiltration  |
| Suspicious PowerShell  | Malware activity   |

